# MesColis.ca

Plateforme canadienne de comparaison de tarifs d'expédition multi-transporteurs.  
Canadian multi-carrier shipping rate comparison platform.

## Structure

```
public/
  index.html   ← Landing page (bilingual FR/EN)
  auth.html    ← Authentication page (login/signup)
```

## Deployment

Deployed on [Vercel](https://vercel.com) as a static site.

- `cleanUrls` enabled → `/auth` serves `auth.html`
- Security headers configured in `vercel.json`

## Local Preview

```bash
npx serve public
```
